OL,3,CUK inflation falls to lowest level in
OL,4,Cnearly three years as energy prices
OL,5,Ccool
OL,7,FThe prime minister welcomed the news,
OL,8,Fdescribing it as a 'major milestone',
OL,9,Fbut will we feel the difference in our
OL,10,Fpockets? ITV News Political
OL,11,FCorrespondent Libby Wiener reports
OL,13,FUK fell to the lowest level in nearly
OL,14,Fthree years in April fuelled by
OL,15,Fcooling energy prices, according to
OL,16,Fofficial figures.
OL,18,FConsumer Prices Index (CPI) inflation
OL,19,Fslowed to 2.3% in April, down ,
OL,20,Faccording to the Office for National
OL,21,FStatistics (ONS).
