OL,7,FIt marks the lowest level since July
OL,8,F2021 when inflation was recorded at 2%
OL,9,F- the Bank of England's target level.
OL,11,FGrant Fitzner, the ONS's chief
OL,12,Feconomist, said: "There was another
OL,13,Flarge fall in annual inflation led by
OL,14,Flower electricity and gas prices, due
OL,15,Fto the reduction in the Ofgem energy
OL,16,Fprice cap.
OL,18,F"Tobacco prices also helped pull down
OL,19,Fthe rate, with no duty changes
OL,20,Fannounced in the budget.
