OL,7,F"Meanwhile, food price inflation saw
OL,8,Ffurther falls over the year. These
OL,9,Ffalls were partially offset by a small
OL,10,Fuptick in petrol prices."
OL,12,FReacting to the latest inflation
OL,13,Ffigures, a Treasury spokesperson said:
OL,14,F"We rightly protected millions of jobs
OL,15,Fduring Covid and paid half of people's
OL,16,Fenergy bills after Putin's invasion of
OL,17,FUkraine sent bills skyrocketing - but
OL,18,Fit wouldn't be fair to leave future
OL,19,Fgenerations to pick up the tab.
